Automating Knowledge Graph Creation

Built a fully configurable tool that scrapes Wikipedia articles, processes them with an LLM, uses custom embedding‑based algorithms to map selected terms to entries in the Wikidata ontology and creates a knowledge graph for them. Developed as part of my university practical course and it delivered cool results - outperforming the official Wikidata API for term matching
